The Ekahau modules provide a Perl interface to the Ekahau Location
Sensing System.

See the perldoc for Ekahau for an overview, and the files ektest.pl
and ektest2.pl for some sample code.

For more information about the project at the University of Michigan
that inspired this work, see:

    http://www.eecs.umich.edu/~wherefid/

For more information about the author, see:

    http://www.suspectclass.com/~sgifford/
